Quote:  When a fellow in business or on a farm draws a prize in "Jimmy Allen's Art Union" he has to go whatever happens to his affairs. [Note. Colonel Sir James Allen is Minister for Defence, and in that capacity controls the ballots which are made use of to fill the drafts after Voluntary recruiting fails].
